        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Now we know that thou hast a devil",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "] ‘It was somewhat of a conjecture before, but now we recognise clear evidence of it.’",
